      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-mesh-convergence-vr",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh convergence validation result — discretization error quantification",
      "description": "Grid convergence index (GCI) study conducted on three systematically refined meshes (1.6 M, 4.8 M, 14.4 M elements) at the 3.5 L/min, 3000 RPM operating point. GCI fine-grid = 2.1% for NIH, confirming discretization error is well within acceptable bounds for MRL 2.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/morrison-gci-study-2024q3"
